accessibility.text: We see the flight attendant really close to conquering Everest. She is dressed for the heavy conditions — a thick jacket with the signature KLM blue peeking out from underneath, a heavy scarf, goggles, and a woollen hat. The soundscape also shifts as we hear the howling of the wind and the crunch of snow.

We cut to the top of the mountain, where the actual KLM crew is standing, already waiting, dressed similarly but proudly showing off their KLM uniforms underneath. We notice a small gap between them — a space left for the KLM protagonist.
